snippet.title: Santria Gameplay Compilation (no sound)
snippet.description:
SANTRIA! is a light-hearted, modern-setting RPG with a strong emphasis on exploration and character interactions and features a tactical battle system, diverse landscapes, and tons of minigames and sidequests.

Access the patron-exclusive teaser demo and many other fun perks when you sign up for our Patreon page at https://www.patreon.com/cheekynauts

Learn more about our games at https://www.cheekynauts.com
